🥁 3. PAD SYSTEM DESIGN

[Piezo Disc]
     |
     +----> 1MΩ Resistor (bleed)
     |
     +----> 1N4148 Diode (protection)
     |
     +----> 10k Resistor (series protection)
     |
     +----> ESP32 ADC pin

🎯 Why this design?

✔ Prevents ADC damage
✔ Reduces noise spikes
✔ Stable velocity reading
✔ Cheap components
✔ Scalable to 16 pads later

